        <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size:12px&quot;&gt;Pain Points — Why Migration Is Needed&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;🔴 &lt;b&gt;Cost&lt;/b&gt;  $42K/th — DD APM $11.8K (295 hosts) + Splunk hot $13.9K (52GB/day, 95% unqueried) + PD $3.9K (65 seats, raw alerts, no dedup)&#xa;🔴 &lt;b&gt;Fragmentation&lt;/b&gt;  3 vendor agents/host · 4 UIs/incident · manual correlation = 8 phút → first hypothesis · 47 PD pages/90s · alert fatigue&#xa;🔴 &lt;b&gt;Visibility gaps&lt;/b&gt;  1% trace sampling misses tail events · cardinality explosion(customer_id) · no service graph · no incident audit trail · Splunk cross-7d &gt;25s&#xa;━━━ Solid = signal flow  ·  ┅┅┅ Dashed = async/manual  ·  Target architecture replaces this $42K stack with $20.9K OTel-first design (↓50.2% cost, ↑ correlation, single Grafana surface)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=10;shadow=0;fillColor=#f8fafc;strokeColor=#e2e8f0;fontColor=#1e293b;fontStyle=1;spacing=10;strokeWidth=2;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="25" y="700" width="2000" height="170" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
